OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773004307
OL,3,CPolice officer who had gun pointed at
OL,4,Chim during arrest 'feared he would die'
OL,6,FBodycam footage shows the moment Jay
OL,7,FConway pulled out a gun and pointed it
OL,8,Fat PC Dan Clayton.
OL,10,FA drug dealer who left a police
OL,11,Fofficer in fear of his life after
OL,12,Fpointing a loaded gun at him following
OL,13,Fa pursuit has been jailed.
OL,15,FPC Dan Clayton found himself "staring
OL,16,Fdown the barrel of a firearm" after he
OL,17,Fattempted arrest Jay Conway in Salford.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
