OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773004307
OL,3,CPolice officer who had gun pointed at
OL,4,Chim during arrest 'feared he would die'
OL,6,FConway was spotted by two other
OL,7,Fofficers moments beforehand riding an
OL,8,Fe-bike and wearing a balaclava in
OL,9,FAlbert Park on Tuesday 20 May 2025.
OL,11,FWhen the officers tried to arrest
OL,12,FConway, he fled onto Great Clowes
OL,13,FStreet where PC Clayton tried to stop
OL,14,Fhim.
OL,16,FPC Clayton said: "As the suspect left
OL,17,Fthe park I happened to be in the right
OL,18,Fplace and just started to chase him.
OL,26,@xD@ROU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773004307
OL,3,CPolice officer who had gun pointed at
OL,4,Chim during arrest 'feared he would die'
OL,6,F"At that point I didn't know he had a
OL,7,Fgun - another 30 seconds and I
OL,8,Fwouldn't have the left the police car."
OL,10,FWhen PC Clayton tried to arrest
OL,11,FConway, he pulled out a gun and
OL,12,Fpointed it at the officer and a member
OL,13,Fof the public.
OL,15,F"Once I saw the gun, I just tried to
OL,16,Ftake cover behind a parked car as
OL,17,Fthere wasn't too much else to hide
OL,18,Fbehind.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773004307
OL,3,CPolice officer who had gun pointed at
OL,4,Chim during arrest 'feared he would die'
OL,6,F"I was staring down the barrel of the
OL,7,Ffirearm and all I could think about
OL,8,Fwas my pregnant wife and that I might
OL,9,Fnever get to see my baby."
OL,11,FOnce PC Clayton got behind cover,
OL,12,FConway dropped the gun ` later
OL,13,Fconfirmed as a viable, loaded pistol `
OL,14,Fand a mobile phone, and fled for a
OL,15,Fsecond time.
OL,17,FGreater Manchester Police's (GMP)
OL,18,FCritical Wanted Unit launched an
OL,19,Finvestigation and used forensic
OL,20,Fanalysis of the phone and CCTV to
OL,21,Fidentify Conway as the suspect.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773004307
OL,3,CPolice officer who had gun pointed at
OL,4,Chim during arrest 'feared he would die'
OL,6,FHe was arrested by armed officers the
OL,7,Ffollowing day in Whalley Range,
OL,8,FManchester.
OL,10,FConway, of Leicester Walk, Salford,
OL,11,Fwent on to plead guilty to possession
OL,12,Fof a firearm, possession of a firearm
OL,13,Fwithout a licence, possession of a
OL,14,Ffirearm with intent to endanger life
OL,15,Fand assault of an emergency worker.
OL,17,FHe also pleaded guilty to possession
OL,18,Fwith intent to supply class A and
OL,19,Fclass B drugs.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773004307
OL,3,CPolice officer who had gun pointed at
OL,4,Chim during arrest 'feared he would die'
OL,6,FHe was sentenced to 14 years in prison
OL,7,Fwith an addition two years on licence
OL,8,Fat Manchester Crown Court on Friday 6
OL,9,FMarch 2026.
OL,11,FHelen Longworth, prosecuting, said:
OL,12,F"PC Clayton heard an officer state
OL,13,Fover the radio that a male was making
OL,14,Foff. He was unaware at this point that
OL,15,Fthe defendant had been seen to have a
OL,16,Ffirearm.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773004307
OL,3,CPolice officer who had gun pointed at
OL,4,Chim during arrest 'feared he would die'
OL,6,F"He caught up with the defendant who
OL,7,Fwas still refusing to stop and
OL,8,Fattempted to take hold of him, which
OL,9,Fcaused him to fall to the ground, at
OL,10,Fwhich point what later proved to be a
OL,11,Fbundle of class A drugs spilled from
OL,12,Fhis hand onto the road.
OL,14,F"Still focused on evading police
OL,15,Fcapture, the defendant got back up and
OL,16,Fagain ran away.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773004307
OL,3,CPolice officer who had gun pointed at
OL,4,Chim during arrest 'feared he would die'
OL,6,F"Pc Clayton ` despite numerous
OL,7,Fwarnings for the defendant to 'stop'
OL,8,Fand advising him that he had a Taser
OL,9,Fwhich was now drawn ` fired the Taser
OL,10,Fat the defendant as he ran to remount
OL,11,Fhis bike.
OL,13,F"The Taser seemed ineffective as the
OL,14,Fdefendant rolled on the floor with two
OL,15,Fhands holding the firearm, pointing it
OL,16,Fdirectly at the officer and causing
OL,17,Fhim to fear for his life."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUyD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
