OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773004307
OL,3,CPolice officer who had gun pointed at
OL,4,Chim during arrest 'feared he would die'
OL,6,FDetective Superintendent Simon Moyles
OL,7,Fsaid: "We identified Conway as the
OL,8,Fsuspect and declared him a critical
OL,9,Ftarget.
OL,11,F"The Force Critical Wanted Unit worked
OL,12,Ftirelessly to bring him to justice,
OL,13,Femploying a wide range of proactive
OL,14,Ftactics.
OL,16,F"The team, alongside the wider SOCG
OL,17,Ffamily at GMP, demonstrated unwavering
OL,18,Fdedication in their efforts to
OL,19,Fapprehend the offender.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
