PN,39710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773004307
OL,3,CPolice officer who had gun pointed at
OL,4,Chim during arrest 'feared he would die'
OL,6,F"Through the use of proactive and
OL,7,Fcovert strategies, we have shown how
OL,8,Frelentlessly we will pursue a target
OL,9,Fonce they are adopted by our team."
OL,11,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,12,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,13,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,14,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,15,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,16,Fbelow...
